Heading to Scottsdale for your BACH? You can book a class with them on the BACH app!

We KNOW finding cute & timeless gifts for a BACH party is hard 😫 But we are loving these favorites from @shanndetrick ❤️ 

Some tips:

💖 Don’t get gifts that have a date to keep them timeless

🥂 Get gifts that are USEFUL as well as cute (think bags, towels, etc)

🥳 Also be sure to check out our stories for more gift ideas from other BACH parties!

#bachelorettegifts #bachparty #bacheloretteideas #bachelorettegiftideas #maidofhonor
